JavaScript

The `gadget-server` package is an auto-generated package of utilities for implementing your Gadget app's backend.

Exports from `gadget-server` are only available in the **backend** of your application, and not on the frontend. For reading and writing
data from your frontend, see the [`@gadgetinc/react`](https://docs.gadget.dev/reference/react) package.

An instance of the [structured logger](https://docs.gadget.dev/reference/gadget-server#loggerinstance) for your Gadget app.

JavaScript

Copy

```

1import { logger } from "gadget-server";
2

3// log at the info level
4logger.info("hello world");
5

6// log an error
7logger.error({ error: new Error("Something went wrong") });
```

```

