If you have a Shopify connection configured, the `connections` object offers helpers for getting a Shopify API client to make calls to Shopify. All functions that create Shopify API clients create an instance of the client from the [`shopify-api-node`](https://www.npmjs.com/package/shopify-api-node) package, pre-configured with the right credentials retrieved from the database.

For example, you can get a Shopify client instance for a given shop ID using `connections.shopify.forShopId`

