Returns an instantiated Shopify API client from [`shopify-api-node`](https://www.npmjs.com/package/shopify-api-node) ready for calling the shop calling the current action or route, if there is one. The current shop is derived from the trigger running the current action or route. If the current shop is unknown, `connections.shopify.current` will be undefined.

