`remixViteOptions` contains the following configuration:

```

remixViteOptions

json
Copy

1{
2  "buildDirectory": ".gadget/remix-dist/build",
3  "appDirectory": "web",
4  "future": {
5    "unstable_optimizeDeps": true
6  }
7}
